title: Luca 3 Piece Wine Set
description:
All the essentials to release your inner Sommelier. Made of polished nickel, these stylish bar accessories deserve to be displayed. Designed in Germany, made in China.

Each set includes one 7  x 3  x 1 ¼ in. corkscrew, one 2 ½  x 2  x ½ in. foil cutter, and one 1  x ½ in. collar
